Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>org.mybatis</groupId>
  <artifactId>mybatis-spring</artifactId>
  <version>1.3.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'org.mybatis:mybatis-spring:jar:1.3.0-SNAPSHOT'

Apache Ivy

<dependency org="org.mybatis" name="mybatis-spring" rev="1.3.0-SNAPSHOT">
  <artifact name="mybatis-spring" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='org.mybatis', module='mybatis-spring', version='1.3.0-SNAPSHOT')
)

Grails

compile 'org.mybatis:mybatis-spring:1.3.0-SNAPSHOT'

Leiningen

[org.mybatis/mybatis-spring "1.3.0-SNAPSHOT"]

SBT

libraryDependencies += "org.mybatis" % "mybatis-spring" % "1.3.0-SNAPSHOT"
